      <img src="https://videocafe.crooksandliars.com/files/imagecache/node_teaser/mediaposters/2020/04/44836.jpg" alt="Stephen Moore Compares Coronavirus Protesters To Rosa Parks" class="card-img-top" />
</a>

    <div class="card-body">
        <div class="card-title">
            <h4><a href="/cltv/2020/04/stephen-moore-compares-coronavirus"  title="Stephen Moore Compares Coronavirus Protesters To Rosa Parks">Stephen Moore Compares Coronavirus Protesters To Rosa Parks</a></h4>
        </div>
        <div class="card-text">
                        In an appearance on the Freedom on Tap Youtube show, Moore discussed helping protesters in Wisconsin, and urged more such “civil disobedience.”        </div>

    </div>
    <div class="card-footer">
        <div class="pull-right">
            Apr 18, 2020        </div>
        <span class="node-submitted">By <a href="/user/scarce" title="View Ed Scarce&#039;s profile and posts">Ed Scarce</a></span>
    </div>
</article>
  </div>

  
  <div class="views-row views-row-3 views-row-odd">
    <article class="node card node-type-media node-display-card" data-nid="158272">
    <a href="/cltv/2020/04/val-demings-and-joy-reid-wonder" title="Val Demings And Joy Reid Wonder Why Florida&#039;s Surgeon General Got The Hook">
      <img src="https://videocafe.crooksandliars.com/files/imagecache/node_teaser/mediaposters/2020/04/44835.jpg" alt="Val Demings And Joy Reid Wonder Why Florida&#039;s Surgeon General Got The Hook" class="card-img-top" />
</a>

    <div class="card-body">
        <div class="card-title">
            <h4><a href="/cltv/2020/04/val-demings-and-joy-reid-wonder"  title="Val Demings And Joy Reid Wonder Why Florida&#039;s Surgeon General Got The Hook">Val Demings And Joy Reid Wonder Why Florida's Surgeon General Got The Hook</a></h4>
        </div>
        <div class="card-text">
                        Florida&#039;s Surgeon General was interrupted and whisked away in the middle of issuing wise advice about COVID-19, which just happens to completely contradict Gov. DeSantis and Donald Trump.        </div>

    </div>
    <div class="card-footer">
        <div class="pull-right">
            Apr 18, 2020        </div>
        <span class="node-submitted">By <a href="/user/aliza-worthington" title="View Aliza Worthington&#039;s profile and posts">Aliza Worthington</a></span>
    </div>
</article>
  </div>

  
  <div class="views-row views-row-4 views-row-even">
    <article class="node card node-type-media node-display-card" data-nid="158268">
    <a href="/cltv/2020/04/joy-reid-sums-maga-re-open-protests" title="Joy Reid Sums Up The MAGA &#039;Re-Open&#039; Protests Popping Up Across The Nation">
      <img src="https://videocafe.crooksandliars.com/files/imagecache/node_teaser/mediaposters/2020/04/44833.jpg" alt="Joy Reid Sums Up The MAGA &#039;Re-Open&#039; Protests Popping Up Across The Nation" class="card-img-top" />
</a>

    <div class="card-body">
        <div class="card-title">
            <h4><a href="/cltv/2020/04/joy-reid-sums-maga-re-open-protests"  title="Joy Reid Sums Up The MAGA &#039;Re-Open&#039; Protests Popping Up Across The Nation">Joy Reid Sums Up The MAGA 'Re-Open' Protests Popping Up Across The Nation</a></h4>
        </div>
        <div class="card-text">
                        In a damning opening segment, the AM Joy host drew parallels to the Brooks Brothers protests and the Tea Party&#039;s origins, and it wasn&#039;t pretty.        </div>

    </div>
    <div class="card-footer">
        <div class="pull-right">
            Apr 18, 2020        </div>
        <span class="node-submitted">By <a href="/user/aliza-worthington" title="View Aliza Worthington&#039;s profile and posts">Aliza Worthington</a></span>
    </div>
</article>
  </div>

  
  <div class="views-row views-row-5 views-row-odd views-row-last">
    <article class="node card node-type-media node-display-card" data-nid="158271">
    <a href="/cltv/2020/04/gov-ron-desantis-cant-mask-his" title="Gov. Ron DeSantis Can&#039;t Mask His Stupidity">
